<I c="Tutorial" i="tutorial" m="tutorials.tutorial" n="tutorial_Beginner_LiveMode_MoneyWork" s="314254">
  <T n="name">0x723DE247<!--String: "Money & Work"--></T>
  <L n="slides">
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_MoneyAndWork_1.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:5bffabd4723fb44e</T>
      <T n="text">0xD2E90117<!--String: "They say <b><font color='#199C2C'>money</font></b> can’t buy happiness, but it sure helps to keep your Sims content! For example, you can use money to upgrade your <b><font color='#199C2C'>house</font></b> and the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Objects</font></b> in it, and pay your <b><font color='#199C2C'>bills</font></b> to keep the power and water on.\n\nFun fact: the Sim currency is called <b><font color='#199C2C'>Simoleons</font></b>!"--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T n="image" p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\Beginner\Beginner_MoneyAndWork_2.png">2f7d0004:00000000:5bffabd4723fb44d</T>
      <T n="text">0xD37AFA2A<!--String: "One of the best ways to make money is joining a <b><font color='#199C2C'>Career</font></b>! Open the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Career panel</font></b>, select <b><font color='#199C2C'>Join a Career</font></b>, and <b><font color='#199C2C'>pick one from the list</font></b> to get one step closer to your first paycheck.\n\nYour Sim will now go to work and earn money! You can see their <b><font color='#199C2C'>schedule</font></b> in the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Career panel</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
    <U>
      <T p="InGame\UI\tutorial\Client\LiveMode\LiveMode_Careers_4.png" n="image">2f7d0004:00000000:2155feca5bfbeed7</T>
      <T n="text">0x57937CB<!--String: "The key to earning big Simoleons is getting <b><font color='#199C2C'>promoted</font></b>. Your Sim will get promoted when they fulfill their Promotion <b><font color='#199C2C'>Requirements</font></b> and max out the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Performance</font></b> bar. Check out the <b><font color='#199C2C'>Career panel</font></b> to see your <b><font color='#199C2C'>progress</font></b>.\n\nUsually, Promotion Requirements are reaching certain <b><font color='#199C2C'>Skill levels</font></b>. To increase your Performance, your Sim should go to work with a <b><font color='#199C2C'>positive Emotion</font></b> and complete their <b><font color='#199C2C'>Daily Task</font></b> before going to work.\n\nYou can read more about Skills and Emotions in other <b><font color='#199C2C'>Live Mode Lessons</font></b>."--></T>
    </U>
  </L>
  <L n="tags">
    <E>Lesson_Beginner_LiveMode</E>
  </L>
